item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - 3 Songs in Lossless (Request)
item.description:
[REQUEST IN LOSSLESS]
Request for these songs in Lossless format

Greetings boys and girls, I couldn't find these tracks in flac or lossless anywhere.

1- Warren G feat. Xzibit and Nate Dogg - Game Don't Wait (Remix) (Prod. by Dr. Dre)
2- Ras Kass feat. Dr. Dre and Mack 10 - Ghetto Fabulous (Prod. by Dr. Dre)
3- Exit Wounds Soundrack or at least DMX - No Sunshine

Thank you very much everyone.
Cheers from Canada!
item.author: DJM
